Varieties of Democracy (V-Dem)
------------------------------
Location: vdem/
Status: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike (CC BY-SA).
        Attribution required; adaptations must be shared alike.
        This tree keeps a country subset of FoRB-relevant indicators only
        (not the full V-Dem release).
Source: https://www.v-dem.net/data/the-v-dem-dataset/
Suggested citation: Coppedge et al., V-Dem Dataset (see V-Dem codebook for the
current recommended citation for the downloaded version).

Extracted summaries
-------------------
Location: extracted/
Derived JSON used by the site pipeline. Contains short excerpts and structured
fields only — not full republication of source documents on country pages.

Large binaries (PDFs, full HTML mirrors, the V-Dem zip) are intentionally
gitignored and can be re-fetched with:

    python3 scripts/archive_download.py
    python3 scripts/archive_extract.py

Committed artifacts are NOTICE, manifest.json, per-country JSON extracts,
extracted/countries.json, and the V-Dem FoRB CSV/JSON subset.
